If you run a private equity fund that seeks investment from state pension f=
unds, you will want to have some sort of governance board that includes rep=
resentatives from those pension funds, not just =E2=80=94=C2=A0not primaril=
y =E2=80=94=C2=A0as a governance tool but also s a marketing tool, a way to=
