m their SEN counterparties. Counterparty relationships between parties effe=
cting digital currency transactions are established on the SEN to facilitat=
e U.S. dollar transfers associated with those transactions.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">SEN transfers occur on a virtually instantaneo=
