nking, borrowing short (taking deposits from crypto firms) to lend long (bu=
ying Treasuries and munis). Silvergate=E2=80=99s assets are real boring nor=
mal stuff, and if=C2=A0its depositors had kept their money at Silvergate, i=
ts bonds would have matured with plenty of money to pay them back. Instead,=
